### Test Book Due Reminder System

# 1. Get books due soon (Admin only)
GET https://localhost:7001/api/borrow/admin/due-soon?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 2. Send manual reminder for specific borrow record (Admin only)
POST https://localhost:7001/api/borrow/admin/1/send-reminder
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 3. Extend borrow (User can extend their own books)
POST https://localhost:7001/api/borrow/1/extend
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "reason": "Cần thêm thời gian để hoàn thành nghiên cứu"
}

